    <item>
      <title>特朗普法官允许对其对法尼·威利斯浪漫史的裁决提出上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trump-judge-allows-appeal-of-his-ruling-on-fani-willis-romance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和七名共同被告获准对佐治亚州法官的裁决提出上诉，该裁决称富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯尽管与一名高级检察官有恋情，但仍可以继续参与州选举干预案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trump-judge-allows-appeal-of-his-ruling-on-fani-willis-romance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>议长约翰逊吹捧共和党在资助协议中移民拘留问题上获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/speaker-touts-gop-wins-on-migrant-detention-in-funding-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，议长迈克·约翰逊周三提倡增加对移民拘留的资助，并削减多样性和气候项目，试图在共和党会议上推销 1 万亿美元的支出协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/speaker-touts-gop-wins-on-migrant-detention-in-funding-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:44:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国钢铁工人联合会支持拜登竞选 2024 年总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/united-steelworkers-endorse-biden-for-president-in-2024-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国钢铁工人联合会正式支持总统乔·拜登，此举支持了他在关键工业摇摆州的竞选活动，一周前他反对出售美国钢铁公司的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/united-steelworkers-endorse-biden-for-president-in-2024-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯将访问以色列，美国希望塑造拉法运动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/blinken-set-to-visit-israel-as-us-looks-to-shape-rafah-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯宣布，他将于本周晚些时候访问以色列，拜登政府希望减轻总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡继续入侵拉法对平民的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/blinken-set-to-visit-israel-as-us-looks-to-shape-rafah-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非部长计划进行彻底变革以结束水危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/south-africa-water-municipalities-to-cede-water-provision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非水务部长森佐·姆楚努 (Senzo Mchunu) 计划彻底改革国家水务行业，并免除市政当局的供水责任，因为距离全国选举还有两个月，供水中断激怒了公民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/south-africa-water-municipalities-to-cede-water-provision</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:06:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴尔的摩希望以每套 1 美元的价格出售数百套空置房屋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/baltimore-wants-to-sell-hundreds-of-vacant-homes-for-1-each</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴尔的摩官员正在决定是否以 1 美元的象征性价格出售用木板封起来的房屋，以吸引房主对饱受犯罪和年久失修困扰的社区进行修缮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/baltimore-wants-to-sell-hundreds-of-vacant-homes-for-1-each</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰总理预计美国最早将于本月提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/ukrainian-premier-sees-us-aid-coming-as-early-as-this-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总理表示，美国受阻的资金最早可能在本月到达，而且为前线招募新兵的规模可能少于军方最初支持的 50 万人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/ukrainian-premier-sees-us-aid-coming-as-early-as-this-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰总理利奥·瓦拉德卡意外辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/irish-prime-minister-leo-varadkar-to-step-down-rte-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰总理利奥·瓦拉德卡 (Leo Varadkar) 突然结束了他在政府的 13 年任期，其中包括两届领导人任期，这段时期经历了经济快速增长、英国脱欧剧变和堕胎合法化，但最终以政党支持率在大选前逐渐减少而告终。即将举行的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/irish-prime-minister-leo-varadkar-to-step-down-rte-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 11:59:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国火车司机将罢工地铁和铁路网络</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/london-underground-drivers-to-strike-again-in-april-and-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于薪资和工作条件方面持续存在争议，火车和地铁司机于 4 月和 5 月宣布罢工，英国铁路网络和伦敦地铁线路将再次陷入停顿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/london-underground-drivers-to-strike-again-in-april-and-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 10:55:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前 F1 车手 Mazepin 在针对欧盟制裁的法庭诉讼中获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/ex-f1-driver-mazepin-wins-court-fight-over-eu-s-russia-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前俄罗斯一级方程式赛车手尼基塔·马泽平 (Nikita Mazepin) 是弗拉基米尔·普京 (Vladimir Putin) 商业盟友之一的儿子，他在反对欧盟制裁的斗争中获胜，这项裁决可能会给其他在乌克兰入侵后受到欧盟惩罚的名门望族带来希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/ex-f1-driver-mazepin-wins-court-fight-over-eu-s-russia-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 09:48:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
